    "updated_at": "2024-06-27T04:04:30Z",
    "body": "Because `$python` is not in \r\n```toml\r\nformat = \"\"\"\r\n[    ](fg:#58A6FF)\\\r\n[](fg:#769ff0)\\\r\n[    ](fg:#58A6FF)\\\r\n[](fg:#769ff0)\\\r\n$directory\\\r\n$git_branch\\\r\n$git_status\\\r\n$time\\\r\n(fg:#3465a4)\\\r\n\\n$character\"\"\"\r\n``` \r\npart in starship.toml file. \r\n\r\nAnd I don't think you configured haskell, golang ... etc. can appear on your prompt.\r\n\r\nThis issue should be closed.\r\n",
    "author_association": "NONE",
